strings.Value: [Pay 500 gold] "I'll try to pick the locks."
[Attack] "Swindler! Hack! Scammer! Time to teach you a lesson!"
"Test your finesse against the finest dwarven locksmithing! Crack the lock, get the prize! Who'll challenge the best dwarven locks of the {g|Five Kings Mountains}Five Kings Mountains{/g}?"
"Here comes the conqueror of locks, scourge of chests {mf|him|her}self! Congratulations, it was a splendid victory!"

"Do you know your way around a lockpick? Why not show off your skills? Here we have three chests, bound with the finest dwarven locks straight from {g|Highhelm}Highhelm{/g}! One attempt is five hundred gold. Open one lock, you get some of your money back. Two locks, and you get back more than you paid. Open all three, and you get the grand prize!"
"Splendid! Come, come, the table's right here. I wish you the best of luck!"
